{
  "text": "I will ask about that in a later session since I don't want to get off the track because it has something to do with the mechanics of time, which I am very puzzled about. But I would ask then, the fifth-density entity in coming here to offer us service as you mentioned penetrated the quarantine. Was this done through one of the windows or was this because of his, shall I say, magical ability? I am Ra. This was done through a very slight window which less magically oriented entities or groups could not have used to advantage.",
